data.title: Statutory Composition & Current Membership
data.text: As mandated by Education Law, noting specific requirements for representation. Appointments approved by the Board of Regents at their most recent meeting. Current members are listed with the dates their terms expire. The list includes the Committee for Athletic Trainers, Committee for Medical Physics, Committee for Perfusion, and the Committee for Professional Assistance. This list does not include extended or auxiliary members who are appointed to serve the State Boards solely on licensure disciplinary and/or restoration and moral character hearing panels.
